messageBody:
I can't access two resources from the files. The first is the
QS_Converter, written for Windows. Is there any source for this script
so that it would work with other platforms? What would be especially
helpful is to simply have the convertor dictionary that it uses.

Second, I can't unzip the PDF dictionaries. I have downloaded both zip
files, but when I try to unzip the second, I get an error.

Paul
